      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. it really captures that sense of \"mission.\" could you expand on that? maybe add a part where he describes the actual people he's seeing—like how they look or act compared to Europeans—to really emphasize why he feels they need this \"civilizing\" influence. make it sound like he's observing something fundamentally different and less developed.",
